item.description: # Lasciate ogne speranza, voi ch’intrate I’m a software quality engineer by day, a perpetual student by night. Trying hard to learn ethical hacking and penetration testing. This is my space, a refuge for the noob. I also play bass when somehow I find myself away from a computer. This is just the start and I really mean the start, I been learning this for just about 3 months. Can’t image the amount of things I’ve yet to learn.
